@elukey , the fields countRows and totalActionTimeMs are both can be seen in Superset DRUID data source.
The DRUID metric spec: 

        "metricsSpec": [
            {
                "type": "count",
                "name": "countRows"
            },
            {
                "type" : "doubleSum",
                "name" : "totalActionTimeMs",
                "fieldName" : "actionTimeInMs"
            }
        ]
